OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain soon
OL,6,Fclearing to scattered showers this
OL,7,Fevening. Srong winds with a chance of
OL,8,Fsevere gales for a while then winds
OL,9,Feasing tonight, with most places
OL,10,Fbecoming dry.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA brighter day with a mixture
OL,13,Fof sunny intervals and occasional
OL,14,Fshowers. Freshening westerly winds.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,17,Fwith some sunny spells on Monday then
OL,18,Fhigh cloud later. Sunny, breezy and
OL,19,Fwarm on Tuesday, cloudier later.
OL,20,FChance of patchy or rain or showers on
OL,21,FWednesday.
